The '''Estación de Fotobiología Playa Unión''' (EFPU) (in English: 'Playa Unión [[Photobiology]] Station') is a non-profit organization, devoted to scientific research about the effects of [[ultraviolet radiation]] on [[aquatic ecosystem]]s.

